name: Silver Crest 15 Liters Air Fryer
description:
• Large Capacity: With a 15-liter capacity, the air fryer can easily cook food for a family or a group of friends.

 

  • Healthier Cooking: The air fryer uses minimal oil, making it a healthier alternative to traditional deep-frying methods.


  • Digital Touch Screen Interface: The air fryer has a sleek and modern design with an easy-to-use digital touch screen interface for convenient operation.

 

  • Powerful Heating Element: The fryer's 1800-Watt heating element can reach temperatures up to 210 degrees Celsius, ensuring that food is cooked evenly and quickly.

 

  • Built-in Timer and Automatic Shut-Off: The air fryer has a built-in timer that can be set up to 65 minutes and an automatic shut-off function to prevent overcooking.

 

  • Accessories Included: The air fryer comes with several accessories, including a baking tray, a fry basket, and a skewer rack, making it versatile and convenient.

 

  • Easy to Clean: The air fryer has a non-stick coating, making it easy to wipe down with a damp cloth, and its parts are dishwasher safe for easy cleaning.
